<para style="q1">

<verse number="3" style="v" />For, see, they wait in ambush to take my life.</para>

<para style="q1">The mighty evildoers gather themselves together against me,</para>

<para style="q1">but not because of my transgression or my sin, Yahweh.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="4" style="v" />They prepare to run at me although I am without fault;</para>

<para style="q1">awake and help me and see.</para>
